{"id":283836,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-无锡11名村民代表在荒地抗议非法拆迁（图/","date":"2013-03-13T09:45:36Z","modified":"2013-03-13T09:45:36Z","title":"维权网 | 无锡11名村民代表在荒地抗议非法拆迁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）本网信息员获悉：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日上午</span><span>，江苏省无锡市滨湖区胡埭镇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名村民代表来到滨湖区政府求见区委书记袁飞，要求区委书记解决胡埭镇政府非法拆迁村民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8000</span><span>亩耕地一事给予答复。区委书记袁飞被村民代表追问得哑口无言，却坚持按照区政府自己制定的“山规”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">178</span><span>号文件办事，不给村民代表有任何法律依据的答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>下午，江苏省无锡市滨湖区胡埭镇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名村民代表在区镇两级政府没有任何答复的情况下，只好来到被非法拆迁的荒地上示威抗议，要求当地政府：落实中央法规，还我人权家园！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名村民代表分别是来自胡埭镇张舍村的苏瑞英，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">280</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇莲杆村东胡巷的胡坤兴，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇莲杆村张英华，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">560</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇莲杆村庄荷英，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">334</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇莲杆村顾仲初，他家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">271</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇莲杆村堵仲良，他家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">375</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇张舍村的堵仕兴，他家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">408</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇张舍村的蒋芝仙，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">275.5</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.5</span><span>亩耕地；来自胡埭镇张舍村的堵兵忠，她家被非法拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span>平方米</span><span>房产和强占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>亩耕地。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-t1QKzwcqnYY/UUAL7DklN6I/AAAAAAAAewE/Ev4wJMSZ1qg/s1600/IMG_20130307_140602.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"245\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-t1QKzwcqnYY/UUAL7DklN6I/AAAAAAAAewE/Ev4wJMSZ1qg/s320/IMG_20130307_140602.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-OR_5nn9pYCA/UUAL7g3wFCI/AAAAAAAAewM/Rdh470E6ikA/s1600/IMG_20130303_144240.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"296\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-OR_5nn9pYCA/UUAL7g3wFCI/AAAAAAAAewM/Rdh470E6ikA/s320/IMG_20130303_144240.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4XXFLbBWt3s/UUAL8D6usfI/AAAAAAAAewU/hPzcKJDD6co/s1600/DSCN3771.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"212\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4XXFLbBWt3s/UUAL8D6usfI/AAAAAAAAewU/hPzcKJDD6co/s320/DSCN3771.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}